  abstract     = {The inner relationships between local graphs in large-scale point clouds is challenging to explore due to its irregular structure. To tackle this issue, we introduce graph transformer network that integrates global features into neighboring points. This network contains general local graph, which is an amalgation between different neighborhoods in the whole point cloud scene. In other words, it represents the most fundamental features in local graphs. Therefore, one point has two features: global factors from corresponding ones in different neighborhoods and its own geometric features.}
